<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Roboto+Mono:ital,wght@0,100..700;1,100..700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Roboto Mono", monospace;
            font-optical-sizing: auto;
            font-style: normal;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start p-6 bg-gray-100">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 p-4">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Unlock Your Potential with Our Courses</h1>
                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
                    We offer a variety of courses to help you advance your career and develop new skills. Join our
                    community of learners and start your journey towards expertise today!
                </p>
                <a href="/coures"
                    class="mt-4 inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded hover:bg-blue-500">
                    Explore Courses
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="md:w-1/2 p-4">
                <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">MERN Stack Development</h2>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            Learn how to build full-stack web applications using MongoDB, Express.js, React, and
                            Node.js.
                            This comprehensive course covers everything from front-end to back-end development.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> 12 weeks</li>
                            <li><strong>Level:</strong> Beginner to Advanced</li>
                            <li><strong>Instructor:</strong> John Doe</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/signup"
                            class="mt-4 inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded hover:bg-blue-500">
                            Enroll Now
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Our Brand Partners</h2>
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                <img src="amazon_11376302.png" alt="Brand 2" class="h-10">
                <img src="amazon_11376302.png" alt="Brand 2" class="h-10">
                <img src="amazon_11376302.png" alt="Brand 2" class="h-10">
                <img src="amazon_11376302.png" alt="Brand 2" class="h-10">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Course Roadmap</h2>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600">
                    <li>Week 1-2: Introduction to MongoDB and Express.js</li>
                    <li>Week 3-4: React Basics</li>
                    <li>Week 5-6: Advanced React and State Management</li>
                    <li>Week 7-8: Node.js and Building REST APIs</li>
                    <li>Week 9-10: Full-Stack Project Development</li>
                    <li>Week 11-12: Deployment and Best Practices</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Projects You'll Work On</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-center">
                Throughout the course, you will create various projects, including a social media application, an
                e-commerce site, and a personal portfolio.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-gray-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Meet Your Instructors</h2>
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-4 space-x-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="man_7854857.png" alt="Instructor 1" class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full mx-auto">
                    <p class="font-semibold">John Doe</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Full-Stack Developer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="man_7854857.png" alt="Instructor 2" class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full mx-auto">
                    <p class="font-semibold">Jane Smith</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">UI/UX Designer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</body>

</html>